<div>
<span class="font-label-caps text-[10px] text-primary uppercase">Month 1-2</span>
<h4 class="font-headline-md text-body-lg mt-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Mini Projects</h4>
<p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant text-sm mt-1">Focus on algorithmic efficiency and fundamental syntax through small-scale automation tools.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Timeline Item 2 -->
<div class="relative group">
<div class="absolute -left-[30px] w-4 h-4 bg-secondary rounded-full ring-8 ring-secondary/10"></div>
<div>
<span class="font-label-caps text-[10px] text-secondary uppercase">Month 3-5</span>
<h4 class="font-headline-md text-body-lg mt-1">Industrial Modules</h4>
